# rules.ctx
- RN-01: Panes require Aircraft (aeronave_id).
- RN-02: New Panes status = ABERTA.
- RN-03: Edit Pane only if ABERTA.
- RN-04: Conclude Pane sets data_conclusao.
- RN-05: RBAC:
  - MANTENEDOR: Register Panes, Add Anexo, Execute Vencimentos/Inspections, Self-Assign responsibility.
  - ENCARREGADO: CRUD (most), Assign any responsibility, Manage Inspections, Extend Vencimentos.
  - INSPETOR: Validate Inspections, Control Vencimentos, View Aircraft Status (No execution rights).
  - ADMINISTRADOR: Manage Efetivo (Users), Global Configs, Register Aircraft.
- RN-06: Vencimentos: Extension requires technical justification; Execution resets counter and disables active extension.
- RN-07: Inspecoes: Open instance generates tasks from templates; Conclusion requires mandatory tasks resolved; Persistent audit of open/close trigram.
- RN-08: Inventory: S/N sync (Adjustment) requires matching slot/item; Item installation sets current location.
